name: Evolving complexity
description: Experimental Tezos-based artwork by @mtyka www.miketyka.com. This NFT will use the better-call.dev API to determine its own primary purchases. Every purchase raises the complexity of the rendered image a notch, reaching 100% when all 50 have been purchased. Additionally the wallets are used to hash a random seed, each additional purchase has the potential to change the image radically. The final artwork will be stable and determined by the unique set of primary buyers.  WARNING: This is a highly experimental piece and may break in the future if the API were to change.
